@startuml
[*] --> LoggedOut

LoggedOut --> LoginAttempt : login attempt (phone number and password)
LoginAttempt --> OwnerLoggedIn : owner credentials valid
LoginAttempt --> EmployeeLoggedIn : employee credentials valid

OwnerLoggedIn --> ChangingProfile : owner updates personal information
EmployeeLoggedIn --> ChangingProfile : employee updates personal information

ChangingProfile --> ProfileChanged : profile updated

LoginAttempt --> PasswordReset : password reset request
PasswordReset --> SecurePasswordReset : secure password reset process

OwnerLoggedIn --> LoggedOut : logout (owner)
EmployeeLoggedIn --> LoggedOut : logout (employee)
@enduml
